# Copy to `.env` (or set in the Cloudflare Pages build env). All build-time, so a
# value change requires a rebuild. See docs/DEPLOY.md.

# Engine implementation behind the SimEngine seam. Only "wasm" exists today; the
# factory defaults to it, so this is optional.
# VITE_SIM_ENGINE=wasm

# Cross-origin URL of the 107 MB simc.wasm (the R2 custom domain, versioned by tag).
# Leave UNSET in dev/preview — the Vite middleware serves it same-origin from
# .engine-cache/. REQUIRED in production (Cloudflare Pages can't host a >25 MiB file).
# Example:
# VITE_ENGINE_WASM_URL=https://engine.example.com/v1205.01/simc.wasm
